Dialogue: 2,0:23:44.99,0:23:49.99,Cart_A_Tre,CARTEL,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,273)\fs26\c&H62CD98&\3c&HF6F5F4&\blur1\bord1.5\clip(7,285,640,289)}Ya estamos a mano
Dialogue: 3,0:23:44.99,0:23:49.99,Cart_A_Tre,CARTEL,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,273)\fs26\c&H33B6AB&\3c&HF6F5F4&\blur1\bord1.5\clip(7,289,640,308)}Ya estamos a mano

